{
  "texts": [
    "Diverse applications of GenAI across aging research.",
    "DNNs can be used to improve epigenetic aging clock accuracy.",
    "Galkin et al. (2021) published the first deep methylation clock [70].",
    "The model performed with MAE of 3.21 years in cross-validation.",
    "de Lima Camillo et al. (2022) constructed a multi-tissue DAC \"AltumAge\" to analyze the non-linear interactions among the CpG sites for age prediction [71]."
  ]
}